01:26:21.334 --> 01:26:23.752
Well, I don't know.
I mean, you guys sell a lot of that stuff.

01:26:23.836 --> 01:26:25.379
People are into it.

01:26:31.761 --> 01:26:33.553
You should know, by the way,

01:26:34.639 --> 01:26:36.139
I hired Brad.

01:26:37.141 --> 01:26:39.893
Yeah, I know. You told me that,
remember? The whole...

01:26:39.977 --> 01:26:43.563
No, sorry,
not for the sex thing or the pool.

01:26:43.898 --> 01:26:46.149
I mean that I hired him for the factory.

01:26:46.818 --> 01:26:49.152
Why? He's a total moron.

01:26:49.237 --> 01:26:51.905
Yeah, I know.
This is going to sound kind of weird,

01:26:51.989 --> 01:26:54.699
but I felt sorry for him.

01:26:55.618 --> 01:26:57.494
Yeah. So did I.

01:27:00.832 --> 01:27:03.291
Well, my car's over here, so,

01:27:04.168 --> 01:27:07.170
I guess I'll see you at the Rotary Club?

01:27:09.090 --> 01:27:10.632
Yeah, I'll see you there.

01:27:15.012 --> 01:27:16.263
Suzie?

01:27:17.598 --> 01:27:19.599
Should we maybe just take one car?

01:27:20.768 --> 01:27:22.644
Yeah. We probably should.

01:27:23.438 --> 01:27:24.604
Yeah.

01:27:26.899 --> 01:27:30.026
I thought that was
a surprisingly tasteful funeral.

01:27:30.111 --> 01:27:34.197
JOEL: Yes, it was. You know, when
I was looking down on him, I thought,

01:27:34.699 --> 01:27:37.993
"This might be the longest
I've ever seen him with his mouth shut."

01:27:38.077 --> 01:27:40.537
SUZIE: Yeah. I didn't expect
that many mourners.

01:27:40.997 --> 01:27:42.706
There were a lot of people there.

01:27:42.790 --> 01:27:43.832
JOEL: Yeah.

01:27:46.794 --> 01:27:51.006
(SINGING) You have been
a friend of mine, rainy day woman

01:27:52.967 --> 01:27:55.594
That woman of mine, she ain't happy

01:27:56.012 --> 01:27:59.306
Till she finds something wrong
and someone to blame

01:27:59.390 --> 01:28:01.057
If it ain't one thing,
it's another one on the way

01:28:01.142 --> 01:28:02.726
(PHONE RINGING)

01:28:04.270 --> 01:28:05.562
ON ANSWERING MACHINE:
Hey. You've reached Cindy.

01:28:05.646 --> 01:28:07.147
I'm not here, so leave a message.

01:28:10.693 --> 01:28:12.110
Where the hell is she?

01:28:14.739 --> 01:28:17.949
How long does it take to get some
goddamned cigarettes around here?

01:28:23.206 --> 01:28:24.706
VALET: Here you are, sir.

01:28:27.293 --> 01:28:28.752
JOE: What the fuck?

01:29:22.515 --> 01:29:24.849
Oh, rainy day woman

01:29:25.643 --> 01:29:29.896
I've never seem to see you for
the good times or the sunshine

01:29:31.440 --> 01:29:35.652
You have been a friend of mine,
rainy day woman

01:29:36.070 --> 01:29:37.195
Woman